cisc275.group3.model.scene

Class SceneWetland

  • java.lang.Object
    • cisc275.group3.model.scene.Scene
      • cisc275.group3.model.scene.SceneWetland
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyScored, PropertyTimed, java.io.Serializable

    public class SceneWetland
extends Scene
implements PropertyScored, PropertyTimed
    Wetland scene/model.

    The Wetland scene implements scoring and timing functions via interface implementations. The ConstructVegetation interface holds component definitions for vegetation objects, and static functions to return fish objects.

    SceneWetland.java

    Author:

      • update

        public void update()
        Overridden from Scene.java abstract method. sceneType from manifest is used to determine how to update each scene model

        For mission related scene models: On approx. 2% of calls, a new instance of a BetaVegetation will be added. The new BetaVegetation can occur anywhere.

        On approx. 5% of calls, the current BetaVegetation will be grown
